    <bioghist id="aspace_d794d4458ee19eefb87f9ea01a8c2366">
      <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
      <p>Founded in 1864, the J. Walter Thompson Company (JWT) is one of the oldest and largest
        enduring advertising agencies in the United States. It is headquartered in New York. The
        London Office first opened in 1899. </p>
      <p>Allen Thomas began at JWT London as a copywriter in 1966; Creative Director, Davidson
        Pearce Agency, 1978-1982; Creative Director, JWT London, 1982; Chairman JWT London 1988;
        Chairman and Chief Creative Officer, JWT Europe 1991.</p>
    </bioghist>
